{"tid":2101762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"G2000「standby更」掠津貼  美心 富臨 I.T照逼放無薪假","createTime":"2020-07-10T04:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T16:17:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"34c8d66f38bfe9a37c1579169469ba6cc37cfbd6","tid":2101762,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/UMQNR526MPSSTUE4L2KJX2MITQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FUMQNR526MPSSTUE4L2KJX2MITQ%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjhYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=2299dd55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200710%2FUMQNR526MPSSTUE4L2KJX2MITQ%2F&h=2ec58839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200710/UMQNR526MPSSTUE4L2KJX2MITQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nG2000「standby更」掠津貼 <br />\n美心 富臨 I.T照逼放無薪假<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ve5IRSiy7fU6GAMZpW0D154tV6c=/1168x759/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/II5NLWDVHKKDZ3AFR2JEGZJBMY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fve5IRSiy7fU6GAMZpW0D154tV6c%3D%2F1168x759%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FII5NLWDVHKKDZ3AFR2JEGZJBMY.gif&h=2f79e404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田北辰創辦的G2000疑誇大員工數目，領取更多資助。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府「保就業」計劃將公帑倒進僱主口袋，僱員飯碗卻未受保障。職工盟發現，有無良僱主以各種剝削員工的招數藉計劃漏洞賺到盡，當中「藍店」富臨、美心和I.T等公司，均迫令員工變散工和放無薪假等，實政圓桌田北辰創辦的縱橫二千（G2000）更自創「standby（預備）更」，疑誇大員工數目，增加領取的津貼額。<br />\n<br />\n職工盟主席吳敏兒表示，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒籲舉報無良企業<br />\n<br />\n職工盟統籌幹事王宇來表示，有份投票通過港版國安法的港區全國人大代表田北辰創辦的G2000，在「保就業」計劃中呈報僱員人數628人，獲批1,687萬元，有投訴指G2000在計劃公佈前已開始解僱員工，逼全職員工放假，並改變佣金制度，取消勤工獎金。在計劃公佈後，G2000不僅保留現職兼職員工，反而擴充兼職人手，新設「standby更」，不用工作但獲支付100元津貼，目的疑為增加員工人數，領取更多資助。<br />\n<br />\n曾出席「撐警飯局」的沈嘉偉旗下服裝品<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n篤人頭」，向「員工」提供合約並供強積金。<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒指僱主以不同招數剝削員工，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n並呼籲公眾舉報。<br />\n<br />\nG2000解釋，<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n富臨、美心、I.T至截稿前未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bDmleFQJRIg9iSa6bWgwI9hrwS4=/709x443/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B2TUOXWCFNTTGXLIWLSGSXSKVA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbDmleFQJRIg9iSa6bWgwI9hrwS4%3D%2F709x443%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB2TUOXWCFNTTGXLIWLSGSXSKVA.gif&h=63a17633&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47cdfcaac6fb4d1dad9ad625ce9173e6a1ff77d3","tid":2101762,"uid":179572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"呢d企業咪無良心囉，政府又攞到明益佢地，係有心益員工洗比舊錢老細先再比員工咩"}]}